&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behaviours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th width=&quot;330&quot; style=&quot;width: 330px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;t is required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;134&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Continuing Personal Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proactive in their own development, willing to commit to lifelong learning and improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;134&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ethical/Legal Awareness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Recognise and act within GDC standards, ethical guidance, information governance and relevant laws.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;134&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaboration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Willing to give and receive feedback effectively and tactfully within the wider dental team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;134&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibility &amp;amp; Integrity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ready to take responsibility for integrity of completed work, although to understand that ultimate responsibility will lie with the Dental Technician.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
